entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You finished the test of speed in time.
entries.journal_entry_description: The pod racer wants to see if you know anything about racing. He has asked you to run a time trial on one of his easier tracks. If you fail to finish a race, you may speak to Draknus or the race droid to start the race over.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The pod racer wants you to prove your ability. Race the course in the required time. Check in with the race timer to start the race.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Check In with the Race Timer to Start Race
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 1 before the timer runs out.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 2 before the timer runs out.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 3 before the timer runs out.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 4 before the timer runs out.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 5 before the timer runs out.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 6 before the timer runs out.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Talk to the race timer to check your time.
